An implementation of the model object 'SDocument Graph'.

The following features are implemented:

  • SDocument
  • STextual DSs
  • STextual Relations
  • STokens
  • STimeline
  • STimeline Relations
  • SSpanning Relations
  • SSpans
  • SStructures
  • SDominance Relations
  • SPointing Relations
